snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance Royal Edition - Launch Trailer [DE]
snippet.description:
The Kingdom Come: Deliverance Royal Edition is now available!

The Royal Edition includes main game and the following additional content:
- Treasures of the Past
- From the Ashes
- Band of Bastards
- The Amorous Adventures of Bold Sir Hans Capon
- A Woman's Lot

#kingdomcomedeliverance #royaledition #awomanslot
